                        <head>218. Summary of Conclusions of a Special Coordination Committee
                                Meeting<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d218fn1">Source: Carter
                                Library, National Security Affairs, Staff Material, Office, Meetings
                                File, Box 14, Folder 19, <gloss target="#t_SCC_1">SCC</gloss>
                                Meeting #140 Held 2/18/79, 2/79. Secret. Initialed by <persName corresp="#p_BZK_1">Brzezinski</persName> at the end of the text.
                                The meeting took place in the White House Situation Room. The
                                minutes of this meeting are ibid.</note>
                        </head>
